high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the rightmost sink.
Open the rightmost cupboard door below the sink and remove the bottle of lotion, then close the cupboard door.
Turn around and walk over to the side of the toilet.
Place the bottle of lotion on the top of the toilet tank in the middle.
Turn left and walk around the toilet to the small grey trash can in the corner of the room.
Pick up the bottle of lotion out of the small grey trash can.
Turn around and walk over to the tub, then turn left and walk over to the towel rack, then turn left to face the toilet.
Place the bottle of lotion on the far edge of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion to the top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Go left towards the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink on the right, take out the bottle, shut the cabinet.
Go right all the way to the tub, turn around and face the toilet.
Place the bottle on the top of the back of the toilet.
Go left all the way to the door, take a right and go to the gray trash can.
Pick up the bottle out of the trash can.
Go right towards the counter, take a right and go all the way to the tub, take a left and face the toilet.
Put the bottle on the top of the back of the toilet to the left of the other bottle.
anns.task_desc: Set two bottles on top of the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right, walk straight, turn left towards the water faucet
Open the right cabinet door, take out the lotion bottle inside, close the cabinet door
Turn right, turn right, turn left towards the bath tub, turn left towards the toilet
Place the lotion bottle on top of the toilet
Turn left, walk straight, turn right, turn left and walk towards the trash can in the corner
Pick up the bottle of lotion from inside the trash can
Turn right, turn right, walk straight, turn left towards the toilet
Place the lotion bottle on top of the toilet next to the other bottle of lotion
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles of lotion on top of the toilet
